{"tid":2065114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科學家：2020年6月21日 中国末日","createTime":"2020-06-15T10:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T03:31:13.000Z","uid":184679,"like":26,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"acc39a8cf08b12835b12068b76d25eb6feef66c6","tid":2065114,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T10:16:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-chinatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org/ii/w1200/s/images.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2020-06-14/900/20200614003648.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-chinatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fii%2Fw1200%2Fs%2Fimages.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2020-06-14%2F900%2F20200614003648.jpg&h=881174b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據科學家Paolo Tagaloguin的說法，長久以來外界針對馬雅曆的解讀，認為2012年12月21日迎來世界末日的說法是錯誤的，他重新計算後，指出世界末日將落在2020年6月21日，也就是說，世界將在下周迎來末日。<br />\n<br />\n綜合英國《太陽報》（The Sun）、《紐約郵報》（New York Post）以及印度媒體「India Times」報導，先前陰謀論者結合馬雅曆法以及古代預言，計算出2012年12月21日是世界末日，儘管當時媒體大篇幅報導，社會上討論度也很高，不過當天並沒有特別的事情發生，世界末日說也逐漸被淡忘。<br />\n<br />\n不過一位名叫Paolo Tagaloguin的科學家上周在社群網站上貼出貼文，指出外界對馬雅曆法的解讀錯誤，如果根據儒略曆（Julian Calendar）來計算，人類現在實際上身處2012年，而非2020年。<br />\n<br />\nPaolo Tagaloguin的說法是，人類自1582年起首度使用格里曆（Gregorian calendar），也就是現今大家慣稱的公曆或陽曆，在此之前不同的地方分別使用馬雅曆以及儒略曆。<br />\n<br />\n如果依照儒略曆的算法，人類轉換成公曆後，每一年都會少算11天，我們必須把這些少算的日子加回去，也就是自公曆廣泛啟用的268年間（1752-2020）乘上11天，再去除365天，總共得出8年。2020年6月21日才是實際上的2012年12月21日。<br />\n<br />\n換句話說，按照Paolo Tagaloguin的算法，下周日就是世界末日。<br />\n<br />\n不過針對世界末日說的說法，美國太空總署（NASA）先前就已表示毫無根據，全部都是虛構的說法。<br />\n<br />\n值得注意的是，報導指出，Paolo Tagaloguin的貼文已經遭到刪除。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20200615000022-260408</code></pre>"},{"pid":"7bcb88b3fec10dbee6f29e8d1e100940c88f5232","tid":2065114,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T10:22:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/flower.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/dog.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/pig.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/mouse.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/rip/cat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e332dcebbce97e5ac760637cc62208905975e5","tid":2065114,"uid":290883,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T10:26:22.000Z","msg":"係真唔係呀，唔好氹我喎？"},{"pid":"33f14db0eb80c567e6584a9ede50664d3568e704","tid":2065114,"uid":8951,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T10:28:13.000Z","msg":"科學家都信依d野？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ca89953e1ed5ad7fa6de162f190d5f131322720","tid":2065114,"uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T10:30:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2019/05/02/php6CPp8u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2019%2F05%2F02%2Fphp6CPp8u.jpg&h=72899d10&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"da2a58725a0320e3b7a4826c54db33477633c56d","tid":2065114,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T16:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef1e4ff5bb2101e32648e83c69e5f07f2e43eb98","tid":2065114,"uid":252142,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T16:34:13.000Z","msg":"是某位皇帝死忌"},{"pid":"e55959778ccddb9c10fa9187c19ef8d12311495a","tid":2065114,"uid":29080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T16:37:46.000Z","msg":"要返工，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dad0b22f1805449550e495db529b194467c1966","tid":2065114,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T16:37:58.000Z","msg":"科學家？ 講埋啲似是而非嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d70702ef82f91b2ba1d2aa9de687bf70aced1f30","tid":2065114,"uid":16775,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020